---
import { Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About us">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="bg-darkblue rounded-lg md:h-80 md:max-h-92 overflow-hidden">
        <Picture
          src="/jumbo1.png"
          alt="/about"
          sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px"
          widths={[200, 400, 800, 1200, 1800]}
          aspectRatio="16:9"
          background="#ffffff"
          fit="cover"
          position="center"
          class="rounded-t-lg opacity-70 overflow-hidden"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1
      class="mb-4 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
    >
      <span
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r to-blue-300 from-blue-700"
        >About</span
      > New World Steelpan Orchestra
    </h1>

    <p class="pb-5">
      New World Steel Pan Orchestra offers a unique opportunity for individuals
      of all ages and skill levels to learn the art of playing the steel pan.
      With their experienced and dedicated instructors, they provide
      personalized instruction to help students develop their technique and
      musical abilities. Their classes are designed to provide a fun and
      engaging learning experience that will leave you with a greater
      appreciation and understanding of Caribbean music and culture.
    </p>
    <p class="pb-5">
      The benefits of learning to play the steel pan go beyond just improving
      your musical skills. It can also have a positive impact on your overall
      well-being. Playing music has been shown to reduce stress, improve
      cognitive function, and increase social connections. By taking classes
      with New World Steel Pan Orchestra, you'll not only improve your musical
      abilities, but you'll also be part of a supportive community that shares
      your passion for music.
    </p>
    <p class="pb-5">
      Whether you're a beginner or an experienced player, there's always room
      for improvement and growth. The expert instructors at New World Steel Pan
      Orchestra are dedicated to helping you achieve your musical goals, whether
      it's learning a new song, mastering a technique, or improving your overall
      musicality. With their welcoming and supportive environment, taking
      classes with New World Steel Pan Orchestra is a great way to develop your
      skills, meet new people, and have fun.
    </p>
  </Container>
</Layout>
